OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTaliban bans women from    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworking at NGOs 'over      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhijab'                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Women's freedoms have been further     
OL,6, curtailed in Afghanistan, after the    
OL,7, Taliban barred them from working for   
OL,8, non-governmental organisations (NGOs). 
OL,10,FThe Islamist rulers said female NGO    
OL,11,Femployees had been breaking Sharia law 
OL,12,Fby failing to wear the hijab.          
OL,14,FIt comes days after female students    
OL,15,Fwere banned from universities - the    
OL,16,Flatest restriction on their education  
OL,17,Fsince the Taliban regained power.      
OL,19,FWomen prevented from going to work told
OL,20,Fthe BBC of their fear and helplessness.
